
2013-01-14	#add by juguofeng
	first version 0.1:
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		<usage> download PPTV source one playlist ts data
		#cd liveTV
		#make
		#./httplive http://61.155.219.118:80/live/5/45/847a4e1e97584d39a961f5604e90c1c4.m3u8?
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
2013-01-14	#add by juguofeng
	[liveTV] version 0.2:
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		<usage> PPTV source one playlist ts live
		#cd liveTV
		#make
		#./httplive
		
		client use "http://host_ip:8080/livetv.ts"
		eg.
			vlc http://localhost:8080/livetv.ts
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
2013-01-16	#add by juguofeng
	[liveTV] version 0.2.1:
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		<usage> PPTV source original url one playlist ts live
		#cd liveTV
		#make
		#./httplive
		
		client use "http://host_ip:8080/livetv.ts"
		eg.
			vlc http://localhost:8080/livetv.ts
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2013-01-18	#add by juguofeng
	[liveTV] version 0.3.0:
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		<usage> PPTV source live, support playlist reloading
		#cd liveTV
		#make
		#./httplive
		
		client use "http://host_ip:8080/livetv.ts"
		eg.
			vlc http://localhost:8080/livetv.ts
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
2013-01-20	#add by juguofeng
	[liveTV] version 0.4.0:
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		<usage> 稳定支持PPTV和搜狐高清源，CNTV源由于重定向种类多，部分支持，其他待测
				（本版本加入了列表重加载、重定向、url绝对地址拼接等功能，但不排除内存泄漏等情况）
		#cd liveTV
		#make
		#./httplive
		
		client use "http://host_ip:8080/livetv.ts"
		eg.
			vlc http://localhost:8080/livetv.ts
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
2013-01-28	#add by juguofeng
	[liveTV] version 0.4.3:
	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		<usage> 增加了一个演示版本的android工程，封装了简单的开始播放的事件接口
		#cd liveTV
		#sh compile.sh android
		自动生成了libhlsjni.so，然后利用Eclipse工具，编译生成apk，打开之后自动播放电视直播
		
		#############################################
		#cd liveTV
		#sh compile.sh linux
		#./httplive
		
		client use "http://host_ip:8080/livetv.ts"
		eg.
			vlc http://localhost:8080/livetv.ts

	--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
